* Breadcrumb icon option (frontend)
* Fix loop news + tags
* Fix Affix logo + header
* Redesign Footer default custom
    * Add section Footer
* Add facebook block footer (frontend)
* Add context "mix" in CMS page
* Add s_page_all in db CMS page
* Add share for mobile (footbar)
* Add quickAccess in breadcrumb (skin)
* Update info for content_css in editor (backend)
* Add lang dropdown (skin frontend)
* Add tabs,tabs-arrow header.tpl (skin frontend)
* Upgrade jquery 1.11.1 => 1.12.0
* Upgrade jquery ui 1.10.3 => 1.10.4
* Add sortable for image galery (backend + frontend)
    * Sort image galery by img_order
    * Add sql for img_order + upgrade sql 2.6.0 => 2.6.5
* Fix bug extend_valid_elements (backend)
* Update img size configuration (default)
* Add about dynamic page
* Add general microdata
* Fix bug library (root)
* Fix bug utf-8 on About plugin (contact.tpl)
* Update youtube tinymce 1.0.1 => 1.1.0
* Change in global less (skin default)
* Add global library (magixcjquery & smarty)
* Add About plugin

